en_695455_0	The Ministry of Agriculture says that measures have been taken to slash the import levy on Big Onions.
en_695455_1	The government announces that the import levy on one kilogram of big onion will be cut by 39 rupees.
en_695455_2	The new measures will be in effect from midnight today.
en_695455_3	Minister of Agriculture P. Harrison stated that this decision was taken to ease the cost of living of the consumers as the price of Big Onions was increased recently.
